data.description: Explore the possibilities at 4815 Gleneagles Drive, a residence strategically situated in Houston, TX 77084. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans 1644 sqft and includes a fully equipped, independent apartment in the back – a fantastic opportunity for generating additional income. Beyond the property's appeal, it is conveniently located near a variety of shopping centers, restaurants, banks, groceries, and more, adding to the overall convenience of daily living. Whether you're seeking a comfortable home or a savvy investment, 4815 Gleneagles Drive offers both in a professional and bustling neighborhood, NEW ROOF 2018,Outside A/C condenser 2018.
